Nollywood darling, Mercy Aigbe has found love again. The actress and film producer has found love four years after parting ways with her erstwhile husband, Lanre Gentry. The Nation was reliably informed that Aigbe has continued to hint at the identity of her new man referring to him as Alhaji the owner. Sources disclosed that Aigbe’s new man is also an entertainment practitioner and big investor in an online streaming platform.   Son of Hollywood actress Regina King commits suicide     I would be bringing a lot to Nigerian Idol 7- IK Osakioduwa     GUS 12: Odudu crowned as 17 other warriors split N23.7m   - Advertisement - It was gathered that her lover has been spoiling her with affection and support with the actress getting the buying-in of her children, Michelle and Olajuwon to remarry. Other sources alleged that the ‘Agbeke’ star’s new man was present at her lavish birthday ceremony, which held a few weeks back and had several celebrities in attendance. Unconfirmed sources alleged that Aigbe had secretly given her consent to become ‘Alhaji’s wife according to Islamic marital rites.